headline.print_headline: Chile Beats NIreland 2-0 in World Cup Warm-Up
headline.main: Chile Beats NIreland 2-0 in World Cup Warm-Up

lead_paragraph: Chile beat Northern Ireland 2-0 on Wednesday night in its final World Cup warm-up game, a match that marked the return of midfielder Arturo Vidal.
